    {
      "name": "Start Session",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-App-Id",
            "value": "{{appId}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-App-Name",
            "value": "{{appName}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-App-Version",
            "value": "{{appVersion}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-Integration-Version",
            "value": "{{integrationVersion}}",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/session/start",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "session",
            "start"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Genera `sessionId`, `nonce` y `deepLink` dentro de Folio. Postman guarda automaticamente esos valores en variables de coleccion.\n\nAlias soportados por la API: `/session/start`, `/session/new` y `/start`.\n\nRequiere `X-Folio-App-Id`, `X-Folio-App-Name`, `X-Folio-App-Version` y `X-Folio-Integration-Version`."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Start Session responde 200', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('sessionId', json.sessionId || '');",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('nonce', json.nonce || '');",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('deepLink', json.deepLink || '');",
              "console.log('Deep link generado:', json.deepLink);",
              "pm.test('Genera credenciales de sesion', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(json.sessionId).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
              "  pm.expect(json.nonce).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
              "  pm.expect(json.deepLink).to.be.a('string').and.include('folio://import');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Import Markdown",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Authorization",
            "value": "Bearer {{nonce}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-App-Id",
            "value": "{{appId}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-App-Name",
            "value": "{{appName}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-App-Version",
            "value": "{{appVersion}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "X-Folio-Integration-Version",
            "value": "{{integrationVersion}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"sessionId\": \"{{sessionId}}\",\n  \"sourceApp\": \"Run2Doc\",\n  \"sourceUrl\": \"https://api.example.com/docs\",\n  \"title\": \"Petstore API\",\n  \"markdown\": \"# Petstore API\\n\\n> [!IMPORTANT]\\n> Generated by Postman collection\\n\\n## Auth\\n\\nUse bearer token.\\n\\n```diff\\n- old\\n+ new\\n```\\n\",\n  \"importMode\": \"newPage\",\n  \"parentPageId\": null,\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"project\": \"Petstore\",\n    \"origin\": \"postman\"\n  }\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/imports/markdown",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "imports",
            "markdown"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Importa un Markdown en Folio usando el `sessionId` y `nonce` generados en `Start Session`.\n\nAntes de lanzar esta request, abre manualmente `{{deepLink}}` para activar la sesion dentro de Folio."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('sessionId') || !pm.collectionVariables.get('nonce')) {",
              "  throw new Error('Primero ejecuta Start Session para generar sessionId y nonce.');",
              "}",
              "console.log('Abre este deep link antes de importar:', pm.collectionVariables.get('deepLink'));"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Import responde 200', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('Import completa correctamente', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(json.ok).to.eql(true);",
              "  pm.expect(json.pageId).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
              "});",
              "if (json.pageId) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('pageId', json.pageId);",
              "  console.log('pageId guardado:', json.pageId);",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Update Page",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [
          { "key": "X-Folio-App-Id", "value": "{{appId}}", "type": "text" },
          { "key": "X-Folio-App-Name", "value": "{{appName}}", "type": "text" },
          { "key": "X-Folio-App-Version", "value": "{{appVersion}}", "type": "text" },
          { "key": "X-Folio-Integration-Version", "value": "{{integrationVersion}}", "type": "text" },
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{nonce}}", "type": "text" },
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"sessionId\": \"{{sessionId}}\",\n  \"title\": \"Updated Document\",\n  \"markdown\": \"# Updated Document\\n\\nContent refreshed by the external app.\",\n  \"importMode\": \"replaceCurrentPage\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/pages/{{pageId}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["pages", "{{pageId}}"]
        },
        "description": "Actualiza el contenido de una pagina que la app importó previamente.\n\nRequiere:\n- `sessionId` y `nonce` generados en `Start Session`.\n- `pageId` de una pagina importada por esta misma app (`{{appId}}`).\n\nRegla de privacidad: solo la app que importó originalmente la pagina puede actualizarla. Las paginas nativas o importadas por otra app devuelven `403 FORBIDDEN`."
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('sessionId') || !pm.collectionVariables.get('nonce')) {",
              "  throw new Error('Primero ejecuta Start Session para generar sessionId y nonce.');",
              "}",
              "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('pageId')) {",
              "  throw new Error('Define la variable pageId con el UUID de la pagina a actualizar.');",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Update responde 200', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('Update completa correctamente', function () {",
              "  pm.expect(json.ok).to.eql(true);",
              "  pm.expect(json.pageId).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
